<% provide(:title, 'About') %>



<div class ="row-fluid">

  <div class="span10 offset1">
        
    <div class="ui-widget-header span10 eventShowTitle"><h2>A no so long introduction to Eventus</h2></div>
    <br>
    <div>
    <div class="span5 ui-widget-content eventShowItems">
      <div style="text-align: center">
      <h3>Idea</h3>
      </div>
      <div class = "span8 offset2" style="margin-left: auto; margin-right:auto ">
	<%=image_tag("eventus.png", :size =>"300x200") %>
      </div>
      <div class="span11">
	<br>
	<p>We believe that people with common interest should get to know each other
	and share their the fun, the thought, the skills each of them
	has. We created this page for people to create events where this idea 
	can be realized.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="span5 ui-widget-content eventShowItems">
      <div style="text-align: center">
      <h3>Functionalities:</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="span11">
      <p>We created some functionalities to give you
      easy ways of creating or finding events.
      <ul>
	<li>You can create, edit or delete an event (oh yes of course you can!).</li>
	<li>Use the Google Maps region to easily set the address of your event. </li>
	<li>You can "like" other users and vote (+1 or -1) for an event.</li>
	<li>When you search for an event, the results will be ordered according to the vote.</li>
	<li>Users can leave comments to the host on the event page.</li>
	<li>After attending an event, attendees can rate the the host.</li>
	<li>If you would like to go to an event, you can add the event to your Google Calendar on just one lick!</li>
	<li>You will get a real time notification if anyone has like you or your event.</li>   
      
      </ul>
      </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    </div>
    
